00:26:35,420 --> 00:26:37,602
Not gonna happen.

482
00:26:38,566 --> 00:26:40,689
What the fuck's that?

483
00:26:40,855 --> 00:26:43,475
What're you doing?
It's like Deliverance in here!

484
00:26:43,550 --> 00:26:44,890
What're you playing at?

485
00:26:47,224 --> 00:26:49,332
I said I wouldn't do the kiss.

486
00:26:50,311 --> 00:26:53,925
McKellen comes to me five minutes before
and drops that bombshell on me:

487
00:26:53,970 --> 00:26:55,431
"Oh, we'd like you to do the kiss!"

488
00:26:55,521 --> 00:26:57,147
Not my cup of tea, mate.

489
00:26:57,463 --> 00:27:01,348
And then all that...
and him, a knight of the realm.

490
00:27:02,296 --> 00:27:04,329
D'you wanna do the end bit
without that?

491
00:27:04,946 --> 00:27:06,647
Oh, he's got the hump.

492
00:27:09,012 --> 00:27:11,888
No understudies, I'm afraid.
