00:27:12,008 --> 00:27:14,462
Sorry about that.
We're nearly finished anyway.

494
00:27:14,507 --> 00:27:16,751
To be fair, there was about
five minutes to go, wasn't there?

495
00:27:16,796 --> 00:27:18,211
All you missed was...

496
00:27:18,738 --> 00:27:20,997
We find out that
me and Fran,

497
00:27:21,102 --> 00:27:24,209
we both have had it off
with Paul, we mentioned earlier.

498
00:27:25,046 --> 00:27:28,961
Paul killed himself 'cause
he was racked with guilt about...

499
00:27:29,263 --> 00:27:31,386
doing it with both of us
behind everyone's back.

500
00:27:32,515 --> 00:27:33,268
So...

501
00:27:36,821 --> 00:27:38,808
She's writing all this down?

502
00:27:38,898 --> 00:27:40,675
That's not gonna be good, is it?

503
00:27:50,817 --> 00:27:53,602
Are you having a laugh?
Is he having a laugh?

504
00:27:55,213 --> 00:27:57,803
Not my audience, so what?

